Honestly, I think people who find cause to attack like those posts were have serious problems in their &quot;walk&quot;.<br>
<br>
The reason for religion is supposed to be a means to bring you inner peace, and to make sense of the world, and your place in it, right?<br>
<br>
How peaceful can it be if you find the need to decide who's more whatever than you are? I think some people only feel better  if by cutting people down, they somehow bolster their flagging sense of self. I'm suspicious of claims that people are blissfully happy when they find the need to attack others. <br>
